ENTRY            F0549   20251215   20260305   20260305       F105
SUBENT        F0549001   20251215   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                 11         26
TITLE      Quasi-free processes in 6Li(3He,palpha)4He reaction at
           low energies
AUTHOR     (M.Zadro,D.Miljanic,M.Lattuada,F.Riggi,C.Spitaleri)
INSTITUTE  (3CRORBZ,2ITYCAT)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,474,373,1987)
FACILITY   (VDGT,2ITYPAD)
DETECTOR   (TELES,SI) Two outgoing particles were detected in
           coincidence. Protons were detected at backward angles
           in a counter telescope consisting of two silicon
           detectors. Two movable silicon detectors for
           alpha-particle detection were put at forward angles
            (15 degree apart) on the other side of the beam
           direction. They were covered by thin Al foils to stop
           scattered 3He particles.
SAMPLE     The targets were made from 6LiF by evaporation onto
           thin carbon backing.
MONITOR    (3-LI-6(HE3,P)4-BE-8,PAR,DA) Protons from the
           6Li(3He,p0)8Be reaction were monitored by the thick
           detector of the proton counter telescope and the
           experimental data on this reaction (see MONIT-REF) were
           used for normalization purposes.
MONIT-REF  (F0001001,C.R.Gould+,J,NSE,60,477,1976)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainty
HISTORY    (20010420C)
           (20251215U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           DATA-ERR1 -> DATA-ERR.
ENDBIB              26
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           29
SUBENT        F0549002   20251215   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                  5          8
REACTION   (3-LI-6(HE3,P+A)2-HE-4,,DA/DA/DE,P/A/P,REL)
           Relative units (No additional information about units.)
ANG-SEC    (ANG1,P)
           (ANG2,A)
EN-SEC     (E-EXC,P)
STATUS     (CURVE,,M.Zadro+,J,NP/A,474,373,1987) Fig.2
HISTORY    (20251215U) SD: BIB updated. EN-ERR -> E-ERR-DIG;
           DATA-ERR -> ERR-DIG.
ENDBIB               8
